0-08-25T11:27:55.000Z","msg":"吊那星原來係親美份子，唔怪得搞到香港亂晒搞衰晒中共同外國經貿外交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97de10f6ebb93b2bab46a919e26b8ebcbb2015e0","tid":2173682,"uid":260806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T11:28:01.000Z","msg":"請主帥親臨前線<br />\n親自抽血"},{"pid":"83ad0ea78fb380d5b82ab48858c0411d38f7ec4c","tid":2173682,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"65e208d7b670f6475aeed3e2753d7c27f66912ff","tid":2173682,"uid":141668,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T11:27:22.000Z","msg":"杜魯門係最撚反共嗰個總統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Truman_Doctrine\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FTruman_Doctrine&d=byei43Pfdy9TlHy68xWwXeSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=1469a816\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Truman_Doctrine</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T11:28:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />奠月蛾反刁"},{"pid":"4f5ff24d239ae2be465bbe99d8368237715e81bb","tid":2173682,"uid":18477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T11:28:38.000Z","msg":"話自己係抗疫主帥<br />\n老矇董開句聲就放人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02257ae01c6a38cb2804928089894f452945e2cc","tid":2173682,"uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T11:29:06.000Z","msg":"確定冇引用錯人物 ?<br />\n<br />\n杜魯門主義（英語：Truman Doctrine）是在美國總統杜魯門任期內形成的美國對外政策。主張：「自由人民正在抵抗少數武裝份子或外來勢力征服之意圖，美國政策必須支持他們。」杜魯門認為，極權主義裹挾自由人民，形成對於國際和平與美國國家安全的威脅。歷史學家埃里克&middot;福納認為，杜魯門主義「成為美國在世界各地援助反共政權（無論其多不民主）的先例，並建立一套針對蘇聯的全球軍事聯盟。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%9D%9C%E9%B2%81%E9%97%A8%E4%B8%BB%E4%B9%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%259D%259C%25E9%25B2%2581%25E9%2597%25A8%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E4%25B9%2589&d=byei43Pfdy9TlHy68xWwXeSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=fc9b2a19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%9D%9C%E9%B2%81%E9%97%A8%E4%B8%BB%E4%B9%89</a>"},{"pid":"e9c9c1b89f84ca9bafbeab72e471e847520cc016","tid":2173682,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T11:29:22.000Z","msg":"心繫美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c630718ecdf04a5eb34555b4f2c4ac472ea00881","tid":2173682,"uid":162073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T11:29:57.000Z","msg":"金乃迪 既金句先係最勁<br />\n勁到講完真人比人連開3槍爆頭"},{"pid":"5877fef74db199254d9fd6725c6edf0e11542215","tid":2173682,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65e208d7b670f6475aeed3e2753d7c27f66912ff","tid":2173682,"uid":141668,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T11:27:22.000Z","msg":"杜魯門係最撚反共嗰個總統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Truman_Doctrine\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FTruman_Doctrine&d=byei43Pfdy9TlHy68xWwXeSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=1469a816\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Truman_Doctrine</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T11:30:48.000Z","msg":"牙娥係暗黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2bc6b2558ea6612ee3bc191609484ea76fdca14","tid":2173682,"uid":75823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"83ad0ea78fb380d5b82ab48858c0411d38f7ec4c","tid":2173682,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"65e208d7b670f6475aeed3e2753d7c27f66912ff","tid":2173682,"uid":141668,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":5,"re